summary: This Level 2 FIRSTLOOK Land Surface product subset for the ARCTAS region contains directional reflectance properties,albedo(spectral & PAR integrated),FPAR,radiation parameters & terrain-referenced geometric parameters, produced using ancillary input from the previous time period.
